{
  "stem": "268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- I think about it many nights when I can't sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if I see anything related to-- to-- to-- to a Holocaust story-- it may be a movie or I read a book or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was separated from her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my life-- if my life changed from the-- since-- at the moment they first bombed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE] on our time in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My life changed 100% again from the time I was separated from my mom and dad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I find myself on my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Here, I'm 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You-- and with a bunch of strange people locked in a box car now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Towards the evening, they load us up in a box car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't know where I was going, what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And people who have-- [CLANKING SOUND] --who knew-- who knew the route-- they were-- like salespeople who traveled around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were looking out the little window on top from the box car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They'd say, oh, I think we passed so-and-so, [NON-ENGLISH] town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oh, my God.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's on the way to Auschwitz-- to Auschwitzen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We already-- there were some rumors then-- then about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And somebody would say, shut up, don't spread doom here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We're not going to-- we're going to-- towards the Czech border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And all-- you know-- all this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I'm sitting here-- and this is a dark box car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you know, the-- and the train is moving and you hear the clickety-clack of the wheels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And my-- I was just hoping to get some water someplace because we were just-- it was a hot day in the sun.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were just laying there all day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And somebody began to cry and to-- and to pray.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
